title: Distributor element schema
description: Distributor element schema generated by the CEDAR Template Editor 2.5.11

propertyDescriptions.distributorType: The type of the distributor of the described dataset (organization, person, or system).
propertyDescriptions.distributorRole: The role of the distributor in bringing the described dataset into existence.
propertyDescriptions.Given name: If the distributor is a person, the personal name(s) of the distributor (e.g., first and optionally middle name in Western languagues, optionally middle and last name in Asian languages).
propertyDescriptions.distributorFamilyName: If the distributor is a person, the surname(s) of the distributor (e.g., last name in Western languagues, first name in Asian languages).
propertyDescriptions.distributor: The full name of the distributor.
propertyDescriptions.personal mailbox: An email address of the distributor.
propertyDescriptions.distributorIdentifier: Information about globally unique identifier of the dataset distributor (an individual, legal entity or system).
propertyDescriptions.distributorAffiliation: The organizational or institutional affiliation of the distributor.

schema:name: Distributor
schema:description: Information about this distributor of the dataset. The Distributor includes preimarily the system doing the distribution, but can include the person or persons responsible as well, for example the person who reformsts the dataset for this distribution.
